soln : using .JS libraries and Frameworks from third-parties or communities

 Libray   ==> we need to call thier functions to get o/p
          ==> we have to oraganize code ourself.


 Framework ==> they call our functions to provide o/p
           ==> struture to our appln
           

Libray 

     ==> jQuery

Frameworks :

    ==> Angular

